Port Assignment
monitor : 3000


To install:
- Install nodejs
- Setup a new mysql database named : soa_trust
- Use db.sql to initialize it.
- Set the mysql username and password in monitor/db/index.php

- run ./install

To start all services (including monitor):
./start

To stop everything:
./stop


All services in scenarios are assigned ports starting with 4101.
Please make sure there are no conflicts.
